Additional notices

Lygodactylus bundles or downloads additional components under their own licenses,
including but not limited to:

- Electron, Node.js runtimes (MIT)
- Python runtime (python-build-standalone; upstream PSF license terms apply to CPython)
- MCP SDK, SQLite drivers, and npm dependencies listed in package.json
- On-demand skill bundles (docx, pptx) published on GitHub Releases
- Bundled skill templates under .claude/skills/ (see per-skill LICENSE files where present)

Runtime artifacts downloaded on first use (Node.js, Python, cliclick, heavy skill bundles)
are fetched from official GitHub Releases of this fork unless you modify download sources
during development.

Features removed from this fork (Feishu/remote control, upstream website, upstream bots)
are not part of the distributed Software above.
